    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "For sale is a vehicle in good condition. The exterior shows minor scratches from regular use but is free of major dents. The interior is clean, with slight wear visible on the driver's seat. All mechanical systems are currently functioning as expected.",
